# Project Discovery Analysis Plan

## Goal Description
Run a new analysis to associate Antigravity conversations with projects in `C:\Temp\repos` and the current workspace.

## Proposed Changes
### Analysis Script
- Run `discover_projects.py`.
- Capture stdout to identify unassociated conversations.

### Reporting
- Update `unassociated_report.md` in `c:\Temp\move_antigravity` (or create a new one if needed) with the latest findings.
- Update `migration_map.json` with any new automatic associations.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Review the generated report and map file.
- Check if the current conversation is correctly associated.
